{"tid":1097004,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果用食肆黎比喻既話 雲加=南記［心心眼emoji]","createTime":"2019-04-08T06:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T06:13:07.000Z","uid":35341,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9796d48ee39c073f4d79c997fba5aa6b5ec91fd9","tid":1097004,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"下午茶 27 蚊 有埋野飲<br />\n一碗河粉兩個送<br />\n仲要送埋紙巾👼<br />\n痴線 根本蝕住做<br />\n就好像雲加的愛 不求回報<br />\n只希望大家開心😍<br />\n<br />\n可惜 佢唔可以度度有分店好似譚咁<br />\n因為大家知佢好食 知佢平 仲有紙巾送<br />\n但好容易比其他食肆吸引去左食其他<br />\n又貴又不好吃<br />\n無好好珍惜佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33970e44d1f305e1b876c778271cd3353f73c67a","tid":1097004,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"麻友 = KFC"},{"pid":"4bcc4d38bc38c62f4bba1ca88093d4c61c0a4942","tid":1097004,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33970e44d1f305e1b876c778271cd3353f73c67a","tid":1097004,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"麻友 = KFC"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:20:34.000Z","msg":"仲要唔好吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4d35bf47dac1525634022b3d776e187d0ab11d","tid":1097004,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bcc4d38bc38c62f4bba1ca88093d4c61c0a4942","tid":1097004,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33970e44d1f305e1b876c778271cd3353f73c67a","tid":1097004,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"麻友 = KFC"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:20:34.000Z","msg":"仲要唔好吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"KFC請啲弱智嘅做廚房，出野慢撚到"},{"pid":"dc4c6227998ae9402b37436609810b7f612d4e79","tid":1097004,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd4d35bf47dac15256